title: American Horror Story: Roanoke - theme music (HQ)
author: American Horror Story: Croatia
comment: Wish there was an opening for this season.
The Return to Roanoke was so much scarier than the Roanoke Nightmare
Kinda sad that Roanoke didnt get an opening sequence. It's one of my favourite seasons and the theme music is by far my favourite, so creepy with the added violins.
I don't get why this season gets so much hate , it's my favourite after asylum ❤
This is so sad and really nostalgic, classic
